*紅毯事件：李畢福出席2014年[[柏林影展|柏林影展]]的電影記者會時，回答關於裸戲問題後，丟下一句讓人摸不著頭腦的話 ("When the seagulls follow the trawler, it's because they think sardines will be thrown into the sea. Thank you very much" （海鷗跟隨漁船，是因為牠們認為漁夫會丟沙丁魚下海，非常感謝。）)即離開會場。到了當晚的紅毯，頭又套著上面寫著"I am not famous anymore"的牛皮紙袋走完全程<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://ent.sina.cn/?sa=t64d3800479v33&pos=19&vt=4 |title=拉博夫柏林影节套纸袋走红毯 |accessdate=2014-02-10 |archive-date=2014-02-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140223003106/http://ent.sina.cn/?sa=t64d3800479v33&pos=19&vt=4 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

*騷擾事件：2014年6月26日，李畢福觀賞[[百老匯|百老匯]]劇碼《Cabaret》時大吼大叫行為失控，疑因大麻藥效發作打人，持續失態，被紐約警方帶上手銬逮捕<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/shia-labeouf-charged-broadway-arrest-715308 |title=Shia LaBeouf Charged Following Broadway Arrest |accessdate=2014-06-27 |archive-date=2014-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140627230559/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/shia-labeouf-charged-broadway-arrest-715308 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://udn.com/NEWS/ENTERTAINMENT/ENT5/8769317.shtml 劇場抽大麻打人 席亞李畢夫遭逮捕]</ref>。

